    "Id": "204351",
    "ThreadId": "41927",
    "Html": "<p>Thanks Damian Schenkelman,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; It worked :) Now I have another question.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; I think the module is loading.. but module is invisible. &nbsp;I am unable to see it. After logging in, the admin view should appear and login view should disappear. I have to keep few variables like role id into some global variables so that I can access them at later stage.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; Pooran</p>",
